01:33:23.430 --> 01:33:23.440
The

01:33:23.440 --> 01:33:25.110
storm

01:33:25.120 --> 01:33:27.470
of the world,

01:33:27.480 --> 01:33:29.750
they're coming in

01:33:29.760 --> 01:33:45.070
