01:33:45.080 --> 01:33:46.630
They need hope.

01:33:50.160 --> 01:33:54.710
It's a breath of fresh air. It's a hope.

01:33:56.600 --> 01:33:58.430
They're wet. Their

01:33:58.440 --> 01:34:07.390
