01:36:40.240 --> 01:36:42.350
there

01:36:42.350 --> 01:36:42.360
is

01:36:42.360 --> 01:36:45.830
a round circle

01:36:45.830 --> 01:36:45.840
with

01:36:45.840 --> 01:36:49.230
