It is

01:38:57.000 --> 01:38:58.950
attached to

01:38:58.960 --> 01:39:08.350
North Korea.

01:40:16.360 --> 01:40:18.630
I see people sitting

01:40:18.640 --> 01:40:20.430
in these houses

01:40:20.440 --> 01:40:23.390
