01:40:44.960 --> 01:40:47.870
These are our brothers and

01:40:47.880 --> 01:40:50.750
sisters in North Korea. They're singing

01:40:50.760 --> 01:40:59.030
without words.

01:41:20.520 --> 01:41:24.470
