01:43:33.680 --> 01:43:35.790
It looks like chalk, but concerning

01:43:35.800 --> 01:43:44.790
these people,

01:43:44.800 --> 01:43:45.910
that

01:43:45.920 --> 01:43:47.870
copper color

01:43:47.880 --> 01:43:50.310
