01:45:04.990 --> 01:45:05.000
was

01:45:05.000 --> 01:45:07.190
like

01:45:07.200 --> 01:45:09.430
nighttime

01:45:09.440 --> 01:45:14.710
with no lights.

01:45:16.720 --> 01:45:19.950
It was attached to China,

01:45:19.960 --> 01:45:22.070
and all of that area

01:45:22.080 --> 01:45:23.950
was

01:45:23.960 --> 01:45:26.070
a complete blackout.

01:45:26.080 --> 01:45:45.310
It looks almost like a black hole.

01:45:45.310 --> 01:45:45.320
There

01:45:45.320 --> 01:45:48.190
is

01:45:48.200 --> 01:45:50.710
no way for them to hear;

01:45:50.720 --> 01:45:54.390
it's a blackout.

01:45:54.400 --> 01:45:57.190
I think what He is

01:45:57.190 --> 01:45:57.200
saying—and

01:45:57.200 --> 01:45:58.430
I don't want to add to or take away

01:45:58.440 --> 01:45:59.470
from

01:45:59.470 --> 01:45:59.480
it—is

01:45:59.480 --> 01:46:00.910
that they've

01:46:00.920 --> 01:46:03.510
