01:46:03.520 --> 01:46:07.310
It's a blackout.

01:46:07.320 --> 01:46:09.350
It's like the Iron Curtain. There's a

01:46:09.360 --> 01:46:12.390
scan of

01:46:12.400 --> 01:46:14.030
this demonic

01:46:14.040 --> 01:46:17.110
skin, of this reptilian demonic

01:46:17.120 --> 01:46:18.350
spirit

01:46:18.360 --> 01:46:20.430
that is up front, glowing, and

01:46:20.440 --> 01:46:24.190
behind it, it's blocking out the Word.

01:46:24.200 --> 01:46:26.950
I see this lizard-like,

01:46:26.950 --> 01:46:26.960
demonic-looking

01:46:26.960 --> 01:46:29.670
thing with the copper

01:46:29.680 --> 01:46:32.670
