01:46:34.800 --> 01:46:36.030
China.

01:46:36.040 --> 01:46:37.470
You attach

01:46:37.480 --> 01:46:39.150
North Korea, and it goes up like this,

01:46:39.160 --> 01:46:41.550
but there was a complete circle of

01:46:41.560 --> 01:46:43.350
blackout.

01:46:43.360 --> 01:46:45.510
You can't hear the Word, is what I believe that

01:46:45.510 --> 01:46:45.520
represents.

01:46:45.520 --> 01:46:47.310
It was

01:46:47.320 --> 01:46:49.270
complete darkness. So

01:46:49.280 --> 01:46:52.390
we're praying into that—a veil that communism

01:46:52.390 --> 01:46:52.400
is

01:46:52.400 --> 01:46:55.230
wadding up. He's done with

01:46:55.240 --> 01:46:57.230
that.

01:46:57.240 --> 01:46:59.350
We have to get rid of that. It's praying

01:46:59.360 --> 01:47:01.630
