01:47:09.640 --> 01:47:12.670
to worship the Father.

01:47:12.680 --> 01:47:15.550
They were making hand gestures

01:47:15.560 --> 01:47:16.830
and

01:47:16.840 --> 01:47:18.550
mouthing it, giving God

01:47:18.560 --> 01:47:20.870
