01:47:20.870 --> 01:47:20.880
to

01:47:20.880 --> 01:47:23.670
be heard

01:47:23.680 --> 01:47:25.910
together

01:47:25.920 --> 01:47:27.670
as a family.

01:47:27.680 --> 01:47:29.630
They

01:47:29.630 --> 01:47:29.640
would

01:47:29.640 --> 01:47:31.670
be

01:47:31.680 --> 01:47:33.910
