01:47:38.000 --> 01:47:40.230
And the Lord said, 'I am

01:47:40.230 --> 01:47:40.240
seeing them,'and

01:47:40.240 --> 01:47:45.070
He's crushing that Iron Curtain.

01:47:45.080 --> 01:47:47.030
That's what we're praying into.

01:47:47.040 --> 01:47:50.150
The snake skin

01:47:50.160 --> 01:47:52.310
is representative of some

01:47:52.320 --> 01:47:53.950
kind of demonic spirit,

01:47:53.960 --> 01:47:56.390
this dragon that's keeping

01:47:57.640 --> 01:48:00.750
Christianity out of there.

01:48:00.760 --> 01:48:02.550
And it was a complete

01:48:02.560 --> 01:48:04.670
black hole

01:48:04.680 --> 01:48:06.830
over North Korea

01:48:06.840 --> 01:48:09.230
all the way up into China.

01:48:12.680 --> 01:48:15.030
It's so dark

01:48:15.030 --> 01:48:15.040
that

01:48:15.040 --> 01:48:18.150
there's not even one light;

01:48:18.160 --> 01:48:26.310
it looked like gross darkness.

01:48:26.320 --> 01:48:34.860
I

01:49:25.400 --> 01:49:31.910
see a great big flathead catfish

01:49:31.920 --> 01:49:34.310
with big

01:49:34.310 --> 01:49:34.320
whiskers—those

01:49:34.320 --> 01:49:36.470
blue

01:49:36.480 --> 01:49:39.310
