01:49:39.320 --> 01:49:42.910
it has the face of

01:49:42.920 --> 01:50:06.400
Kim Jong-un.

01:51:00.800 --> 01:51:03.950
Coming up through the south, I see a

01:51:03.960 --> 01:51:07.150
light coming on the land. I see the

01:51:07.160 --> 01:51:10.110
green grass coming

01:51:10.110 --> 01:51:10.120
and

01:51:10.120 --> 01:51:12.950
the parting of that

01:51:12.960 --> 01:51:15.590
darkness. It's coming from

01:51:15.600 --> 01:51:18.150
the south,

01:51:18.160 --> 01:51:20.430
from the

01:51:20.440 --> 01:51:23.990
southeast, and it's spreading up

01:51:24.000 --> 01:51:25.910
like when you would turn the

01:51:25.920 --> 01:51:28.830
light on in a cartoon.

01:51:33.920 --> 01:51:36.190
Everything that

01:51:36.190 --> 01:51:36.200
was

01:51:36.200 --> 01:51:38.710
blacked out

01:51:52.920 --> 01:51:55.230
is getting color. The

01:51:55.240 --> 01:51:57.630
green grass is coming; flowers are

01:51:57.640 --> 01:52:13.770
coming. Their clothes are wet. There will be a major revival in Nevada. I see shaking in Nevada and the casinos

01:52:13.770 --> 01:52:13.780
closing. There is going to be so much glory. There will be glory where sin abounds; My grace

01:52:13.780 --> 01:52:18.030
does much more abound. And there will be glory spots in the least likely places. They are

01:52:18.030 --> 01:52:18.040
in LA and Portland, Oregon. There will be great shaking in your soil, all the way up. I

01:52:18.040 --> 01:52:21.150
see it again; a great shaking for an awakening. Clear up to Seattle, a great shaking to

